04:34.875 --> 04:36.643
How long has your
family been here?

04:36.644 --> 04:38.378
How far back do you guys go?

04:38.379 --> 04:42.882
I'm half Indian, half African,
and my mother has been

04:42.883 --> 04:44.050
here four generation.

04:44.051 --> 04:46.386
Four generations, that's
starting out in the...

04:46.387 --> 04:47.687
Late 1700s.

04:47.688 --> 04:48.221
Wow.

04:48.222 --> 04:50.089
Who built this neighborhood?

04:50.090 --> 04:58.090
Construction started in 1830s
in a Portuguese colony.

04:59.900 --> 05:03.235
And it started in 1864 but they

05:03.236 --> 05:05.037
lost a lot of power in 1996.

05:05.038 --> 05:06.072
Confused?

05:06.073 --> 05:07.440
Let's take a step back.

05:07.441 --> 05:08.775
The Persians were the first

05:08.776 --> 05:11.378
major power to set up here back

05:11.379 --> 05:13.746
around 975 a.D. Expanding their

05:13.747 --> 05:17.116
empire onto the strategically
positioned island.

05:17.117 --> 05:22.121
Then the Portuguese used
Zanzibar a hub for their slave

05:22.122 --> 05:23.523
trade and spices.

05:23.524 --> 05:28.361
Then they did the same
ultimately with the British who

05:28.362 --> 05:33.099
ruled from them.

05:33.100 --> 05:33.501
1964, revolution.

05:33.502 --> 05:35.067
As with most revolutions, the

05:35.068 --> 05:39.271
days following were
violent, chaotic and ugly.

05:39.272 --> 05:41.441
After overthrowing the mostly

05:41.442 --> 05:43.275
Arab government, reprisals.

05:43.276 --> 05:46.112
It wasn't intended for a

05:46.113 --> 05:49.115
revolution where more than 3,000

05:49.116 --> 05:51.618
Arabs and Indians were
moved out of this country.

05:51.619 --> 05:52.752
But your family stayed?

05:52.753 --> 05:54.320
My family stayed.

05:54.321 --> 05:56.055
Why?

05:56.056 --> 06:00.259
There was no money for
the family to move out.

06:00.260 --> 06:00.994
Tough times?

06:00.995 --> 06:08.801
Very tough times.

06:08.802 --> 06:12.805
In about two hours from stone

06:12.806 --> 06:16.643
town, this is John Biani,
a tiny fishing village.

06:16.644 --> 06:24.644
Here the first revolutionaries
met from an independent

06:25.986 --> 06:27.420
Zanzibar.

