situation back then?

06:37.698 --> 06:40.166
Well, it wasn't good.

06:40.167 --> 06:41.534
Basically it was English...

06:41.535 --> 06:43.836
Arabs in the middle and then the

06:43.837 --> 06:45.872
Africans way, way at the bottom.

06:45.873 --> 06:48.841
And it was a form of
apartheid, you know.

06:48.842 --> 06:52.344
Was this village sort of a
center for revolutionary...

06:52.345 --> 06:53.946
This village was important in

06:53.947 --> 06:57.116
terms of the political support
prior to the revolution.

06:57.117 --> 06:58.718
When my grandfather and my

06:58.719 --> 07:02.955
grandmother stayed right here

07:02.956 --> 07:06.526
