field right over there.

07:06.527 --> 07:07.327
That's where they would have

07:07.328 --> 07:08.828
their meetings to raise support

07:08.829 --> 07:14.801
for the African people,
their it into identity.

07:14.802 --> 07:22.802
The objective was to give
identity to Zanzibar.

07:25.979 --> 07:28.548
Well, this is the house.

07:28.549 --> 07:34.488
They are preparing a
wonderful lunch for us.

07:42.863 --> 07:44.731
