09:36.509 --> 09:37.344
Yeah.

09:37.345 --> 09:39.879
How to preserve all these
things, find balance?

09:39.880 --> 09:43.515
To me, I see Africa as a whole.

09:43.516 --> 09:49.221
I see a very interesting timing.

09:49.222 --> 09:49.823
Optimistic?

09:49.824 --> 09:51.357
I'm very optimistic and think

09:51.358 --> 09:53.025
we have a lot of great people.

09:53.026 --> 09:54.293
And given the opportunity, I

09:54.294 --> 09:56.696
think they can put a lot on the

09:56.697 --> 09:58.130
table, not only for themselves

09:58.131 --> 10:00.700
